{"tid":1580204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"波洛西接見黃之鋒及何韻詩　稱港府應調查警方濫用暴力","createTime":"2019-09-19T03:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T05:27:02.000Z","uid":181997,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b230f9deeeb7f98cd1e63788018cce3d74394226","tid":1580204,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"美國國會將審議《香港人權與民主法案》，獲跨黨派支持。眾議院議長波洛西聯同跨黨派議員，以及香港眾志黃之鋒及藝人何韻詩等人，一同舉行記者會。<br />\n波洛西認為，特區政府撤回修訂逃犯條例是好消息，但並不足夠，港人值得擁有在基本法保障下的高度自治及自由，特區政府應該履行承諾，給予港人普選，並調查警方濫用暴力。她又強調，美國不應該讓商業利益，凌駕政策。<br />\n黃之鋒形容，今日是標誌性的一日，感謝美國跨黨派的共識，證明香港永遠不是孤單，港人會繼續戰鬥，直至得到自由及民主。何韻詩亦感謝美國國會，在香港目前的困難時刻，支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXyv6RZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXyv6RZ.png&h=1256f0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">波洛西（左三）接見黃之鋒（右二）及何韻詩（左二），表示港府應調查警方濫用暴力。</span>"},{"pid":"f9c1cb768f746bd22960ccc97cd424bd44a80b39","tid":1580204,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=d4588be4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url